---
const pageTitle = "Plancha360 | Outdoor cooking, made social";
const pageDescription =
	"Plancha360 is a premium-accessible outdoor cooking brand built around shared meals, warm gatherings, and the urge to cook together.";
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>{pageTitle}</title>
		<meta name="description" content={pageDescription} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<main class="site-shell">
			<section class="hero">
				<div class="eyebrow">Plancha360</div>
				<h1>Outdoor cooking that feels like the center of the evening.</h1>
				<p class="lede">
					Plancha360 is a premium-accessible outdoor cooking brand built for long tables, friends, and the kind of meals
					people remember because they happened together.
				</p>

				<div class="hero-actions">
					<a class="button button-primary" href="#waitlist">Join the waitlist</a>
					<a class="button button-secondary" href="#product">Explore the product</a>
				</div>

				<div class="trust-row" aria-label="Key brand promises">
					<span>Social first</span>
					<span>Premium but accessible</span>
					<span>Built to last</span>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="intro-grid" aria-label="Brand summary">
				<article>
					<h2>Show, don’t tell.</h2>
					<p>
						The website should make people feel the scene before they read the specs: warm fire, easy hosting, and a product
						that turns cooking into a shared ritual.
					</p>
				</article>
				<article>
					<h2>Built for the first customer.</h2>
					<p>
						Home hosts first. Then events. Then hospitality. The message stays simple: this is the grill people gather around.
					</p>
				</article>
			</section>

			<section id="product" class="section">
				<div class="section-heading">
					<p class="eyebrow">The product</p>
					<h2>One object. Multiple reasons to gather.</h2>
				</div>

				<div class="card-grid">
					<article class="card">
						<h3>Model 900</h3>
						<p>900 mm diameter · 5 mm grill plate · hip-high format for shared outdoor cooking.</p>
					</article>
					<article class="card">
						<h3>Model 700</h3>
						<p>700 mm diameter · 5 mm grill plate · the smaller version for tighter patios and easier setups.</p>
					</article>
					<article class="card">
						<h3>Why it matters</h3>
						<p>It is not just hardware. It is the anchor of the evening: cook, talk, serve, stay.</p>
					</article>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="section split">
				<div>
					<p class="eyebrow">What it solves</p>
					<h2>People buy the feeling, then the function.</h2>
				</div>
				<ul class="benefits">
					<li>Turns cooking into a social event instead of a solo task.</li>
					<li>Feels premium, but not cold or exclusive.</li>
					<li>Simple enough to understand in seconds.</li>
					<li>Credible enough to justify the price.</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="section" id="waitlist">
				<div class="section-heading">
					<p class="eyebrow">Waitlist</p>
					<h2>Be first when Plancha360 opens.</h2>
					<p>
						For now, the main goal is interest collection. This form is the starting point for launch demand and future orders.
					</p>
				</div>

				<form class="waitlist-form">
					<label>
						Name
						<input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your name" />
					</label>
					<label>
						Email
						<input type="email" name="email" placeholder="you@example.com" />
					</label>
					<label>
						What are you planning?
						<select name="intent">
							<option>Hosting at home</option>
							<option>Buying as a gift</option>
							<option>Event / rental interest</option>
							<option>Just curious</option>
						</select>
					</label>
					<label class="full-width">
						Message
						<textarea name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Tell us what you want to cook, host, or build around Plancha360."></textarea>
					</label>
					<button class="button button-primary full-width" type="submit">Join the waitlist</button>
				</form>
			</section>

			<section class="section faq">
				<div class="section-heading">
					<p class="eyebrow">FAQ</p>
					<h2>Clear answers, no supplier noise.</h2>
				</div>

				<details open>
					<summary>Who is this for?</summary>
					<p>People who host, love outdoor cooking, and want something that feels premium without becoming a luxury flex object.</p>
				</details>
				<details>
					<summary>Can I order directly?</summary>
					<p>That is the next phase. The site should support direct checkout later, but the immediate launch goal is waitlist interest.</p>
				</details>
				<details>
					<summary>Will rentals be available?</summary>
					<p>Yes, later the site can expand to event rentals once the core brand and product flow are established.</p>
				</details>
			</section>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	:global(:root) {
		color-scheme: light;
		--bg: #f5efe6;
		--panel: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
		--panel-strong: #fff9f1;
		--text: #1f1a17;
		--muted: #665b54;
		--border: rgba(31, 26, 23, 0.12);
		--accent: #b8552d;
		--accent-2: #2d4b45;
		--shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(51, 32, 18, 0.12);
		font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
	}

	:global(html) {
		background:
			radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(184, 85, 45, 0.18), transparent 40%),
			radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(45, 75, 69, 0.14), transparent 34%),
			var(--bg);
		color: var(--text);
	}

	:global(body) {
		margin: 0;
		min-height: 100vh;
	}

	.site-shell {
		max-width: 1120px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 32px 20px 72px;
	}

	.hero,
	.section,
	.intro-grid article {
		background: var(--panel);
		backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 28px;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow);
	}

	.hero {
		padding: 56px 40px;
	}

	.eyebrow {
		margin: 0 0 12px;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.18em;
		font-size: 0.76rem;
		color: var(--accent);
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	h1,
	h2,
	h3,
	p {
		margin-top: 0;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem);
		line-height: 0.92;
		max-width: 11ch;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

	.lede {
		font-size: 1.18rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		max-width: 58ch;
		color: var(--muted);
		margin-bottom: 28px;
	}

	.hero-actions {
		display: flex;
		gap: 14px;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		margin-bottom: 28px;
	}

	.button {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: 14px 20px;
		border-radius: 999px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 700;
		border: 1px solid transparent;
	}

	.button-primary {
		background: var(--text);
		color: white;
	}

	.button-secondary {
		border-color: rgba(31, 26, 23, 0.18);
		color: var(--text);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.42);
	}

	.trust-row {
		display: flex;
		gap: 12px;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.trust-row span {
		padding: 10px 14px;
		border-radius: 999px;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		color: var(--muted);
		font-size: 0.92rem;
	}

	.intro-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 18px;
		margin: 18px 0;
	}

	.intro-grid article,
	.section {
		padding: 28px;
	}

	.section {
		margin-top: 18px;
	}

	.section-heading {
		max-width: 62ch;
		margin-bottom: 24px;
	}

	.card-grid,
	.benefits {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 16px;
	}

	.card,
	.benefits li,
	details {
		padding: 22px;
		border-radius: 20px;
		background: var(--panel-strong);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	.card p,
	.intro-grid p,
	.section p,
	details p,
	li {
		color: var(--muted);
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.split {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
		gap: 24px;
		align-items: start;
	}

	.benefits {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr;
	}

	.waitlist-form {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 16px;
	}

	label {
		display: grid;
		gap: 8px;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	input,
	select,
	textarea {
		width: 100%;
		box-sizing: border-box;
		padding: 14px 16px;
		border-radius: 16px;
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
		font: inherit;
		color: var(--text);
	}

	.full-width {
		grid-column: 1 / -1;
	}

	.faq {
		display: grid;
		gap: 12px;
	}

	details summary {
		cursor: pointer;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.intro-grid,
		.card-grid,
		.split,
		.waitlist-form {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		h1 {
			max-width: none;
		}

		.hero {
			padding: 40px 24px;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.site-shell {
			padding-inline: 14px;
		}

		.section,
		.intro-grid article,
		.hero {
			border-radius: 22px;
		}

		.button {
			width: 100%;
		}
	}
</style>
